title: Crash of ios app
body:
Hi:
I have use the libgdx1.5.0 to generate a default project and package it with Robovm Tools. when install done, I start the app , it can be start up,and the bad logic picture shows with red background, and do nothing, about 4 or 5 minutes, the app quit itself, I can not figure out why this happen, and there is no problem with the Simulator. Someone encounter this? Here is the software config:

Eclipse:4.4.1
Java: Java SE 8(1.8.0)
libgdx: 1.5.0
robovm: 1.0.0-beta
Android: 5.0
Ipad Air: 7.0.4

Because I have no idea of how to analysis the crash, I just attach them,here is the crash log
